227
00:12:20,320 --> 00:12:21,559
In that case,

228
00:12:21,559 --> 00:12:23,279
the first half of this proverb

229
00:12:23,279 --> 00:12:25,159
makes sense now.

230
00:12:25,159 --> 00:12:27,919
