236
00:12:45,759 --> 00:12:47,120
Let's rest first.

237
00:12:59,960 --> 00:13:01,080
Have some.

238
00:13:03,960 --> 00:13:04,840
You too.

239
00:13:14,196 --> 00:13:16,416
(Guangju Hall)

240
00:13:20,240 --> 00:13:21,039
Qing Xing.

241
00:13:23,120 --> 00:13:24,399
