♪The tenderness you gave♪

266
00:14:50,759 --> 00:14:51,759
Dear,

267
00:14:51,759 --> 00:14:52,559
you're awake.

268
00:14:53,559 --> 00:14:54,559
Still hurt?

269
00:14:54,559 --> 00:14:55,639
Any discomfort?

270
00:14:56,159 --> 00:14:57,279
I'll go get a doctor.

271
00:14:57,279 --> 00:14:58,080
