♪Our blaze♪

278
00:15:18,720 --> 00:15:22,816
♪How to hide it♪

279
00:15:23,552 --> 00:15:27,392
♪The crowd frequently separated us♪

280
00:15:27,392 --> 00:15:30,464
♪Watching the story end♪

281
